  "title_extended": "Alfa AWUS036AX USB WiFi 6 Adapter – Dual-Band High Power",
  "short_description": "WiFi 6 USB Adapter, dual-band 2.4 GHz / 5 GHz, 802.11ax, chipset Realtek™ RTL8832BU",
  "description": "AWUS036AX is the WiFi 6 (802.11ax) 2x2 dual-band 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz USB adapter. The AWUS036AX USB adapter incorporates highly integrated Realtek™ RTL8832BU WLAN chipset, with support for 802.11ax standard. It works in two frequency bands 2.4 GHz / 5 GHz on a 802.11ax standard using 2x2 MIMO technology. The USB adapter is backward compatible with standard 802.11a/b/g/n/ac and is equipped with two RP-SMA female connectors including dual-band 5 dBi dipole omni antennas.",
  "detailed_description": [
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "AWUS036AX is the WiFi 6 (802.11ax) 2x2 dual-band 2.4 GHz and 5 GHz USB adapter. The AWUS036AX USB adapter incorporates highly integrated Realtek™ RTL8832BU WLAN chipset, with support for 802.11ax standard. It works in two frequency bands 2.4 GHz / 5 GHz on a 802.11ax standard using 2x2 MIMO technology. The USB adapter is backward compatible with standard 802.11a/b/g/n/ac and is equipped with two RP-SMA female connectors including dual-band 5 dBi dipole omni antennas."
    },
    {
      "heading": "Key features:",
      "text": "- RTL8832BU WiFi 6 chipset\n- USB-A connector support USB 3.2 GEN 1\n- RP-SMA external antenna connector\n- High-gain dual-band 2.4 GHz +5 GHz detachable dipole antenna\n- LED indicator"
    }
  ],
